1.9.2.name: connect20/Infinity_Mailcall_Shipping_method
1.9.2.description: The Want It Now extension facilitates the dispatching of purchased products via a courier once the online payment is processed. Mailcall Couriers pick up your online retail products and deliver them to your customer&#x2019;s door within 3 hours of the order confirmation.
